A buoy (MAD-1522) reported a POSSIBLE_SUBMARINE object at a distance of 0.89 km from Rostock, with a magnetic anomaly of -27.7. This event necessitates immediate classification and verification.

fields.dataset_info:
[{"tablename":"text.sql","select":"SELECT
  MMSI,
  Event_Timestamp,
    destination,
    Status,
    operational_status,
    system_status,
    longitude,
    latitude
FROM (
  SELECT
    MMSI,
    Event_Timestamp,
    destination,
    Status,
    operational_status,
    system_status,
    longitude,
    latitude,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY MMSI ORDER BY Event_Timestamp DESC) as rn
  FROM defense.marine_vessel_status
) ranked
WHERE
  ranked.rn = 1","columns":[{"name":"mmsi","type":"STRING","alias":"mmsi","isdim":true},{"name":"event_timestamp","type":"STRING","alias":"event_timestamp","isdim":true},{"name":"destination","type":"STRING","alias":"destination","isdim":true},{"name":"status","type":"STRING","alias":"status","isdim":true},{"name":"operational_status","type":"STRING","alias":"operational_status","isdim":true},{"name":"system_status","type":"STRING","alias":"system_status","isdim":true},{"name":"longitude","type":"DOUBLE","isdim":false,"alias":"longitude"},{"name":"latitude","type":"DOUBLE","isdim":false,"alias":"latitude"}]},{"tablename":"defense.german_navy_fleet","parent_tablename":"text.sql","join_pairs":[["mmsi","mmsi"]],"join_exprs":[],"join_type":"left outer join","columns":[{"name":"class","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"class"},{"name":"name","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"name"},{"name":"mmsi","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"german_navy_fleet mmsi"},{"name":"jahr_in_dienst","type":"INT","isdim":false,"alias":"jahr_in_dienst"},{"name":"besatzung","type":"INT","isdim":false,"alias":"besatzung"}]}]

[{"tablename":"text.sql","select":"SELECT
  mmsi,
  event_timestamp,
  latitude,
  longitude,
  speed,
  course,
  status,
  destination
FROM (
  SELECT
    mmsi,
    event_timestamp,
    latitude,
    longitude,
    speed,
    course,
    status,
    destination,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY mmsi ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC) as rn
  FROM
    defense.ais_events_ice
) AS ranked_events
WHERE
  rn = 1","columns":[{"name":"mmsi","type":"BIGINT","alias":"mmsi","isdim":true,"useroverrodeisdim":true},{"name":"event_timestamp","type":"STRING","alias":"event_timestamp","isdim":true,"cast":"TIMESTAMP"},{"name":"latitude","type":"DOUBLE","alias":"latitude","isdim":false},{"name":"longitude","type":"DOUBLE","alias":"longitude","isdim":false},{"name":"speed","type":"DOUBLE","alias":"speed","isdim":false},{"name":"course","type":"DOUBLE","alias":"course","isdim":false},{"name":"status","type":"STRING","alias":"status","isdim":true},{"name":"destination","type":"STRING","alias":"destination","isdim":true}]},{"tablename":"defense.ships","parent_tablename":"text.sql","join_pairs":[["mmsi","mmsi"]],"join_exprs":[],"join_type":"left outer join","columns":[{"name":"mmsi","type":"BIGINT","isdim":false,"alias":"ships mmsi"},{"name":"ship_name","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"ship_name"},{"name":"vessel_type","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"vessel_type"},{"name":"imo_number","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"imo_number"},{"name":"call_sign","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"call_sign"},{"name":"flag","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"flag"},{"name":"length_m","type":"DOUBLE","isdim":false,"alias":"length_m"},{"name":"beam_m","type":"DOUBLE","isdim":false,"alias":"beam_m"},{"name":"gross_tonnage","type":"DOUBLE","isdim":false,"alias":"gross_tonnage"},{"name":"year_built","type":"INT","isdim":false,"alias":"year_built"}]}]
